Show the logo tidymass.

tidymass_logo.Rd

The tidymass logo, using ASCII or Unicode characters

tidymass_logo(unicode = l10n_info()$`UTF-8`)

Arguments

unicode

Whether to use Unicode symbols. Default is TRUE on UTF-8 platforms.

Value

A ASCII log of tidymass

Author

Xiaotao Shen shenxt1990@outlook.com

Examples

tidymass_logo()
#> Thank you for using tidymass!
#> Version 1.0.6 ( 2022-09-19 20:08:40 )
#> More information: tidymass.org
#> ⬢ __  _    __   .    ⬡           ⬢  .
